{"type": "article", "id": 20005, "title": "适合两种材料的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-31T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185113KtEqiXfFWbgHxOCP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>意大利设计师 Martino Gamper 设计了一种可选两种材料加工的椅子 St Mark，他想让一种椅子同时用于室内室外，橡木做的椅子用在室内，带小孔的金属材料的椅子用在室外，适合咖啡厅或餐厅这类需要保持统一风格的地方。椅子的靠背和下面的腿连成一体，有曲线的优雅，很简单。有多种不同的颜色，也同样适合居家空间。 </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150318RNa8Es750rjgTZ2S.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"527\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150319RM02bTqceQIK9ynV.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150319KCekrWRhTuVbzNci.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150320amVIc9oeKSirMjlh.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}